*** All
	- A distant server where to put encrypted files

*** Windows
	- GnuPG4Win (or GnuPT)

*** GNU/Linux
	- python
	- GnuPG
	- iw
	- traceroute
	- scrot
	- streamer
	All of these tools should be into your repositories:
		Debian based: aptitude install python gnupg net-tools iw traceroute scrot streamer
